                            <comment id="12994397" author="kmarsden" created="Mon, 14 Feb 2011 18:06:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is the 10.5 patch. Again some manual merge even merging from 10.6. Running tests now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12994568" author="kmarsden" created="Mon, 14 Feb 2011 23:43:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ported fix to 10.6 and 10.5, reclosing issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
